<P ALIGN="justify">	Allow me to introduce myself.  My name is <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/~xorrin/" title="Xorrin Aarikis" target="_blank">Xorrin</a> Aarikis, Heyokah and Scaled Mystic of the mighty Iksar Empire, and this is my domain.  Welcome to <B>Vazaelle.NET</B>, home of the <I>Knights of the Green Mist</I> and the <I>Norrath Alliance Treaty Organizatoin (<a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="N.A.T.O." target="_blank">N.A.T.O.</a>)</I>!

<P ALIGN="justify">	For those of you who just happened to stumble upon our humble domain by sheer fate, allow me to elaborate&amp;#8230;<UL><LI>Vazaelle is the best server in <A HREF="http://www.EverQuest.com/" TARGET="_blank" TITLE="EverQuest&#8482; ~ You're in our world now!">EverQuest&amp;#8482;</A>.<LI><I>The Knights of the Green Mist</I> is the oldest Guild on the Vazaelle Server.<LI>And finally, <I>N.A.T.O.</I> is the largest Alliance of Guilds on the Vazaelle Server!<LI><B><I>Vazaelle.NET</I></B> is the unofficial official site for the Vazaelle Server.</UL>

<P ALIGN="justify">	If you have not already had a chance to do so, I would like to invite you to <A HREF="http://www.vazaelle.net/user.php?op=register&module=NS-NewUser" TITLE="Create an account on Vazaelle.NET&#8230;">REGISTER</A> with us.  To do so is 100% FREE, and your information will never be given to anyone for any reason (short of a legal court order).  Doing so will enable you to <A HREF="http://www.vazaelle.net/user.php?op=loginscreen&module=NS-User" TITLE="Log in to Vazaelle.NET&#8230;">LOG IN</A> and enjoy the many hidden treasures within our realm.  When creating an account, please keep in mind the following two very important items:<OL><LI>Use only the FIRST NAME of your primary <a href="http://www.EverQuest.com/" title="EverQuest™" target="_blank">EverQuest</a>&amp;#8482; Character as your User Name.  (If you do not have one, then any unique name will do.)<LI>You <U>must</U> leave a valid E-Mail address.  (The system will E-Mail you a random temporary password, which you will be able to change when you log on.  You will not be able to log in without a valid E-Mail address.  Rest assured, I HATE SPAM - You will never get it from us!)</OL>

<P ALIGN="justify">	If you are already a member, simply <A HREF="http://www.vazaelle.net/user.php?op=loginscreen&module=NS-User" TITLE="Log in to Vazaelle.NET&#8230;">LOG IN</A> and you will be able to access the special Members Only sections of the site.

<P ALIGN="justify">	Finally, if you would like additional information or require special assistance with anything relating to <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="Knights of the Green Mist" target="_blank">KGM</a>, <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="N.A.T.O." target="_blank">NATO</a>, or Vazaelle.NET, simply drop me a line.  My E-Mail address is <A HREF="mailto:xorri&#110;&#064;&#118;azaelle.net?SUBJECT=Vazaelle.NET / KGM / N.A.T.O.&BODY=Hail, Xorrin!">xorri&#110;&#064;&#118;azaelle.net</A>.

