<td><font class="pn-title"><a href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=index&amp;catid=1">Raid Announcements</a>: <a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=47&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">KGM Raids and Events for the 3-day weekend!</a></font><br>
<font class="pn-normal">Just a heads-up that <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="Knights of the Green Mist" target="_blank">KGM</a> is putting together some non-stop raiding and special events for this weekend, starting tomorrow (Friday for you guys back in the states). <br />
<br />
Everyone in <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="N.A.T.O." target="_blank">NATO</a> is welcome to join in on anything and everything. Some of the biggies we'd like to do, but will need your help with, include a couple LDoN RAIDS (up to 32 members each) for various levels, some Planes Raids (old and PoP - the goal here is to get everyone in NATO who can come flagged!), hopefully FINISH MY EPIC - only 3 small raids to go!, and special events such as Dynamic Multi-Zone Quests, Aide Stations, Zone Parites, etc. <br />
<br />
Spread the word! Hope to see you all there! Events will be run as people are available to fill the minimum numbers needed for each event, but there should be something happening at pretty much any time of day. I will post schedules as early as possible on the Vazaelle.NET calendar and NATO forums. <br />
<br />
Hope to see you all there!</font><br>
<font class="pn-sub">Published Oct 10, 2003 - 10:16 AM</font>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</p>
<p>
<table width="95%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tr>
<td><font class="pn-title"><a href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=index&amp;catid=3">Site Updates</a>: <a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=46&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">Server Updates</a></font><br>
<font class="pn-normal">I am in the process of updating the server, as well as the site.  Over the next couple of days, please let me know if you encounter any odd errors.  These changes will affect ALL sites hosted on the vazaelle.net server (RBD, DoS, etc).<br />
<br />
The current phase of updates includes updating the Linux operating system, as well as the various modules which allow the server to function.  Perl, MySQL (which is what 99% of the site is based on, including the message boards for all sites hosted here), etc.  Sercuity updates are the biggie, as well as brining the OS itself up to the current release version.<br />
<br />
The next couple of phases will include updating PostNuke to the latest release, also addressing several security issues, as well as improving many features, new and old.<br />
<br />
The third phase will include updating the message boards to a PN-specific better-supported version of the phpBB2 module.  The one currently running really isn't supported, and is pretty much dead in the water for development.  The new version is a seperate project on the same Forum software, but has much more development and support, as well as more of the orginal options and features in the non-PN version of phpBB2.  The only real difference you should notice here is the addition of new features to the forums.<br />
<br />
The final phase of the updates will include the cosmetic touch-ups, such as changing the Theme of the site, splitting the <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="Knights of the Green Mist" target="_blank">KGM</a>, <a href="http://www.vazaelle.net/" title="N.A.T.O." target="_blank">NATO</a>, and Vazaelle Server aspects of the site into 3 new sites, as well as adding more graphics, and general layout changes.<br />
<br />
Again, if you notice ANYTHING wrong with the site, please let me know ASAP!<br />
<br />
- X</font><br>
<font class="pn-sub">Published Sep 30, 2003 - 02:19 AM</font>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</p>
