<td><font class="pn-title"><a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=42&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">Jinxed Sponsored Open FUN Event on Vazaelle!!!</a></font><br>
<font class="pn-normal">Come one Come ALL.<br />
<br />
Jinxed is sponsoring an open event. The purpose is to have some fun, maybe drink a little, and give away prizes to those who prove themselves worthy.<br />
<br />
<b>WHO:</b> All players level 5-18, bring an alt or start one up!<br />
<b>WHAT:</b> Quest event with over 10K Plat in prizes for the winning group and other worthy players.<br />
<b>WHERE:</b> Vazaelle Server, Greater Faydark Zone<br />
<b>WHEN:</b> Friday August 8th 8:30 PM EST<br />
<b>WHY:</b> Jinxed is all about Fun and Adventure, and many people are so tired of XP Grinding so WHY NOT!<br />
<br />
<b>Details:</b><br />
This will be a quest event. Players will have to find items in and around the Greater Faydark Zone. The story will be played out in shout and in the chat channel JINXEDEVENT. All players level 5-18 are welcome. Completion of the event will require grouping. JINXED players will be on hand to give out free buffs of various sorts and to play parts in the event. If you do not want to play the event but still want to be a part of it, other buffers are more than welcome!<br />
<br />
The winning group will be awarded lavish prizes, everyone who participates is invited to the post event party with free food, beverages, and buff renewals. We also have prizes for those players who show exceptional effort, energy, and enthusiasm (or just look real good!). Weâ&amp;#8364;&amp;#8482;ll be making lists and checking them twice. <b>Right now the prize pool is worth just over 10K and we are still adding to it!</b><br />
<br />
So please join us. Give up one evening of XP grinding, raiding, or farming and just have some FUN!!!!!!!!<br />
<br />
<br />
And let you friends and guildmates know. Feel free to copy this post to any other guild or <a href="http://www.EverQuest.com/" title="EverQuest™" target="_blank">EQ</a> info site you frequent. Thanks.</font><br>
<font class="pn-sub">Published Jul 31, 2003 - 07:00 PM</font>
